I"<p>The xTechSearch program is voluntary and open to all interested traditional and nontraditional businesses that meet the eligibility requirements.&nbsp; Each company is limited to submit only one (1) white paper for this&nbsp; competition.</p>
<p>The Phase I proposal must be a white paper describing the novel technology concept, innovative application concept and integration with one or more of the Army&rsquo;s technology focus areas as defined under the "Overview" tab.</p>
<p>The Phase I proposal must be submitted via the Challenge.gov portal as a single searchable PDF file containing:</p>
<ul>
<li>Title</li>
<li>Author(s)</li>
<li>Army Technology Focus Area:&nbsp; Choose from the eight (8) Technology Focus Area(s) described below that proposal addresses</li>
<li>Keyword(s): Provide up to ten (10) keywords that describe the technology</li>
<li>Abstract: Provide an abstract (up to 250 words)</li>
<li>White Paper: Technology proposal concept, no greater than 1000 words (not including title, author(s), keywords, abstract, company bio, graphs, figures or images).&nbsp; The word limit on the White Paper submission will be strictly enforced.</li>
<li>List of prior SBIR awards in the past 5 years:&nbsp; Include Date award received, Funding organization, Phase of awards, and Topic Title awarded</li>
<li>Company Biography (Optional): Company background information, up to 1 page</li>
</ul>
<p>Follow these steps to complete the Challenge.gov submission form:</p>
<ol>
<li>Make sure you are logged into youe Challenge.gov account.&nbsp; If you do not have a Challenge.gov account, please create one by clicking the red "Login" button in the top right of the page.</li>
<li>Once you have logged into your account, ensure you are on the xTechSearch page and click the red "Submit" button in the top right of the page to bring up the submission form.</li>
<li>Enter your title in the <strong>Title</strong> field.</li>
<li>Enter your absract in the <strong>Description</strong> field.</li>
<li>Enter your keywords in the <strong>Tags</strong> field.</li>
<li>Upload your white paper and optional company biography in a single PDF by clicking on <strong>Browse File</strong> under <strong>Attachment</strong>.</li>
<li>Select all appropriate <strong>Technology Focus Areas</strong> for your submission.</li>
<li>Respond to the four <strong>SBIR-STTR questions</strong>.</li>
<li>Provide the appropriate contact information under&nbsp;<strong>Point of Contact</strong>.</li>
<li>Click the blue "Submit" button at the bottom of the submission form page.</li>
</ol>
<p>The submission package must be provided to the xTechSearch Challenge.gov portal by 11:59 PM PST on <strong>31 December 2018&nbsp;</strong>(2:59 PM EST on 1 January 2019).&nbsp;Submissions received after the deadline will not be considered.</p>
